attributes.Long form description: The student begins by withdrawing the four unscrews from the base frame. Then he removes the brackets from the middle tray and the top tray in order to remove them. The student then stands up the base frame to remove the brackets from the third tray and remove it. The student then begins to disassemble the base frame, first removing the side bars to manually detach the base frame.The student finishes by placing all the pieces in order on the table.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, thank you for agreeing to take part in our study.
In front of you, you will see the Rashult IKEA bathroom cabinet.
Your task for now will be to please disassemble it.
You may now begin. Thank you.
